      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The engine runs smoothly, the transmission shifts as it should, and all major mechanical systems are in solid working order. While there are some minor cosmetic imperfections on the exterior and light wear on the interior upholstery, the car is overall clean and presents well. It has a full service history and is ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately without any urgent repairs needed.",
